name: Le test de dactylographie de qualité supérieure
name_original: Le test de dactylographie de qualité supérieure
description:
Type french words as fast as you can !

How To Play :

Use your keyboard  to type as many words as you can in 1 minute ! 
You have to type "play" in the text zone to launch a game. 

Le test de dactylographie de qualité supérieure is a student prototype I realize with my friend Bastien Mahaut : we had a theme : "minimalist", and a constraint: to make FX.
